>> total time: 8 hours 10 minutes

Combine @uncooked old fashioned oats{1/3%cup}, @unsweetened vanilla almond milk{1/3%cup}, @light artificially sweetened yogurt{1/3%cup}, @mixed berries{3/4%cup}, @lemon zest{1%tsp}, @cinnamon{1%pinch}, @vanilla{1/4%tsp}, @chia seeds{1%Tbsp}, and @salt{1%pinch} in a #medium jar or large glass{}; stir, cover and refrigerate overnight. Garish with @almonds{1%Tbsp}; serve.
